nt-bold text-brand-navy mt-8 mb-4",children:"1. Information We Collect"}),h.jsx("p",{className:"text-slate-600 mb-4",children:"We collect information from you when you request a quote, book a service, or contact us via our website, phone, or email. The personal information we collect might include your name, address, email address, phone number, and details regarding your moving requirements."}),h.jsx("h3",{className:"text-xl font-bold text-brand-navy mt-8 mb-4",children:"2. How We Use Your Information"}),h.jsx("p",{className:"text-slate-600 mb-4",children:"We may use your information to:"}),h.jsxs("ul",{className:"list-disc pl-6 text-slate-600 mb-6 space-y-2",children:[h.jsx("li",{children:"Provide you with an accurate quote for our services."}),h.jsx("li",{children:"Carry out our obligations arising from any contracts entered into by you and us."}),h.jsx("li",{children:"Notify you of changes to our services."}),h.jsx("li",{children:"Process payments and maintain our accounts and records."})]}),h.jsx("h3",{className:"text-xl font-bold text-brand-navy mt-8 mb-4",children:"3. Data Security"}),h.jsx("p",{className:"text-slate-600 mb-4",children:"We are committed to ensuring that your information is secure. In order to prevent unauthorized access or disclosure, we have put in place suitable physical, electronic, and managerial procedures to safeguard and secure the information we collect online and offline."}),h.jsx("h3",{className:"text-xl font-bold text-brand-navy mt-8 mb-4",children:"4. Sharing Your Information"}),h.jsx("p",{className:"text-slate-600 mb-4",children:"We will not sell or rent your information to third parties. We will not share your information with third parties for marketing purposes. We may pass your information to our third-party service providers (e.g., payment processors) for the purposes of completing tasks and providing services to you on our behalf."})]})]}),h.jsxs("div",{children:[h.jsxs("div",{className:"flex items-center gap-4 mb-8 border-