bility. However, our liability for loss or damage is limited to the terms of our insurance policy. We are not liable for damage to items packed by the customer unless the damage is caused by our negligence. Valuable items (jewelry, money, important documents) should be transported personally by the customer."}),h.jsx("h3",{className:"text-xl font-bold text-brand-navy mt-8 mb-4",children:"4. Cancellations and Postponements"}),h.jsx("p",{className:"text-slate-600 mb-4",children:"If you cancel or postpone your move, you may be subject to a cancellation fee depending on the notice given. Please contact us as soon as possible if your plans change."}),h.jsx("h3",{className:"text-xl font-bold text-brand-navy mt-8 mb-4",children:"5. Payment"}),h.jsx("p",{className:"text-slate-600 mb-4",children:"Payment must be made in full upon completion of the move unless otherwise agreed in writing prior to the moving date. We accept cash, bank transfers, and major credit/debit cards."}),h.jsx("div",{className:"mt-12 p-6 bg-brand-light rounded-2xl border border-slate-200",children:h.jsxs("p",{className:"text-slate-700 font-medium",children:["If you have any questions regarding our Privacy Policy or Terms & Conditions, please contact us at ",h.jsx("a",{href:"mailto:info@ccmsupremeremovals.com",className:"text-brand-accent hover:underline",children:"info@ccmsupremeremovals.com"})," or call us at ",h.jsx("a",{href:"tel:01582292303",className:"text-brand-accent hover:underline",children:"01582 292303"}),"."]})})]})]})]})})})]})}const vE=[{question:"How much does a house removal cost?",answer:"The cost of a house removal depends on several factors including the size of the property, the distance of the move, the amount of furniture, and whether packing or storage services are required. The best way to get an accurate price is to request a free quote through our website.",icon:h.jsx(C5,{className:"text-brand-accent",size:24})},{question:"Do you provide packing services?",answer:"Yes. CCM Supr